      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like strength though. it just feels like i'm being forced to endure something that doesn't have an end. everyone says \"stay strong\" like it's some kind of achievement, but it just feels like i'm being punished for something i didn't even do. i just want it to be still. i want the noise and the hurting to just... stop. permanently.",
